questions: What is the name of the organization with the ID {organization_id}?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX uuid: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#urn:uuid> SELECT  ?name WHERE {{ ?organization a syn:Organization; syn:id '{organization_id}'^^uuid:; syn:name ?name. }}

questions: Who is associated with the organization with the ID {organization_id}?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX uuid: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#urn:uuid> SELECT  ?first ?last WHERE {{ ?organization a syn:Organization; syn:id '{organization_id}'^^uuid:; syn:id ?organizationId. ?encounter a syn:Encounter; syn:organizationId ?organizationId; syn:patientId ?patientId. ?patient a syn:Patient; syn:id ?patientId; syn:first ?first; syn:last ?last. }}
